    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone willing to put in a little work. The engine and transmission are functional, though you can expect some minor leaks and the typical wear associated with a car of this age. Cosmetically, the exterior has several noticeable scratches and some fading paint, while the interior shows significant wear on the upholstery and a few cracked plastic trim pieces. It has been recently serviced, but it will likely need new tires and a brake pads soon. This is an honest, high-mileage car that gets the job done without any frills.",
