    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this distinguished vehicle, a testament to engineering excellence and attentive ownership. This model offers a refined driving experience, characterized by a responsive powertrain and a meticulously preserved interior. Having undergone a rigorous multi-point inspection, the vehicle demonstrates consistent performance and structural integrity. It serves as an ideal selection for the professional seeking a sophisticated, reliable transport solution that maintains a commanding presence on the road. This is a premier opportunity to acquire a well-maintained asset that balances luxury with proven durability.",
      "price": 34500.0,
