    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it's been such a joy to drive. It's in really solid shape\u2014super reliable and has clearly been well-cared for over the years. It\u2019s got plenty of life left in it and is ready for its next adventure with a new owner. Perfect for someone looking for a dependable car that still looks and feels great on the road. Come take it for a spin, you'll love it!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a pinnacle of analog performance, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L straight-six featuring individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS timing. The drivetrain is anchored by a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. Mechanically, this unit is sorted with recent rod bearing service and a reinforced rear subframe to address common chassis fatigue. The suspension geometry remains precise, delivering the communicative feedback and 50/50 balance this platform is renowned for. While the exterior displays honest patina from enthusiast use, the powertrain exhibits excellent compression and linear power delivery across the entire rev range.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Clean title. Regular maintenance completed. No mechanical issues. Ready for immediate pickup.",
      "price": 29500.0,
