    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, perfect for someone looking for a dependable car without the brand-new price tag. Everything runs smoothly, and I\u2019ve taken care of the basics to keep it ready for the road. I\u2019m happy to chat or let you take it for a spin\u2014just shoot me a message! Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel of this beauty!",
      "price": 29500.0,
