    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This unit remains mechanically sharp, with the VANOS system recently serviced and the rear subframe reinforced\u2014a critical preventative measure for this chassis. The engine utilizes its factory individual throttle bodies for immediate transient response, paired with a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. Performance is further bolstered by a variable M differential lock and a suspension geometry that retains its factory-spec turn-in precision. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the mechanical vitals are excellent, showing strong oil pressure and a linear power delivery to the 8,000 RPM redline. This is a robust, turn-key example for the purist who prioritizes drivetrain integrity and chassis dynamics",
